General.Name: MYT Netherlands Parent BV
General.Description: MYT Netherlands Parent B.V., through its subsidiary, Mytheresa Group GmbH, operates a luxury e-commerce platform for fashion consumers in Germany, the United States, rest of Europe, and internationally. The company offers womenswear, menswear, kids wear, and lifestyle products. MYT Netherlands Parent B.V. sells clothes, bags, shoes, accessories, and fine jewelry through online and retail stores. The company serves high-income luxury consumers. MYT Netherlands Parent B.V. was founded in 1987 and is based in Munich, Germany.
